title: Cuisinart Smart Stick® Variable Speed Cordless Rechargeable Hand Blender (CSB-300) Demo Video
description: Introducing a new hand blender that’s one of the most multifunctional food prep tools in any kitchen. This Smart Stick™ comes with an electric knife attachment that lets users effortlessly carve a roast or slice a loaf of bread, a 3-cup chopper for nuts, cheese and garlic, and a chef’s whisk for meringue and whipped cream.
